dataList.content: Stubb's death did this to you, didn't it...?

dataList.title: E.G.O Floreciente::Arpón de Gas
dataList.content: Pip would have said as such! He crushed his own heart and gave himself to me, so that he would be freed from his guilt!

dataList.title: E.G.O Floreciente::Arpón de Gas
dataList.content: Be not so cruel to a mere child, Ishmael! Cast your eyes upon me!

dataList.title: E.G.O Floreciente::Arpón de Gas
dataList.content: His broken heart led him to me, and I have freed him from his guilt to the best of my abilities!

dataList.title: E.G.O Floreciente::Arpón de Gas
dataList.content: But what did you do? Nothing! The least you could have done was to volunteer to row in Pip's place on that fateful day!

dataList.title: E.G.O Floreciente::Arpón de Gas
dataList.content: The fault lies with you, Ishmael!

dataList.title: E.G.O Floreciente::Arpón de Gas
dataList.content: Yet I am the evil here?
